## Risk Register

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| Self-modification creates infinite update loops | Meta-rules have a priority ordering and a maximum-iterations bound (Kleene fixed-point converges in O(witness count) iterations). The hand-evaluator detects non-convergence and errors. |
