## Specification Reference
- **Primary**: ADR-FERR-030 (wavelet matrix convergence — attribute interning is prerequisite)
- **Supporting**: NEG-FERR-007 (field entropy analysis: attribute H₀ ≈ 2.5 bits/byte, 34x compressible)
