| LIVE iteration order change | Roaring iterates in ascending u32 order, which matches BitVec's `iter_ones()` order. The `live_datoms()` iteration order is preserved. Verified by proptest. |
| Set operations API mismatch | Roaring uses `|=`, `&=`, `-=` overloads vs BitVec's named methods. Mechanical translation. ~10 call sites total. |

